Package: echosmart-gateway
Architecture: armhf arm64 amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-venv, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: mosquitto, i2c-tools
Description: EchoSmart IoT Gateway for precision agriculture
 Edge-computing gateway that reads environmental sensors (temperature,
 humidity, CO₂, light, soil moisture) on a Raspberry Pi and synchronises
 data with the EchoSmart cloud backend. Includes local alerting, SQLite
 cache for offline resilience, and MQTT publishing.
